reviewText: The four Discs in this set are among the the epitomes of the art, not only dramatically entertaining but also comedic in spots. The performers are beautiful, artistic, skilled and great at ad-lib. I'm quite happy I purchased this and plan to look for others of the "golden age 4-packs".
a set of disks which came as a surprise to me me as I opened it. I wasn't thinking along the lines they were, but very good just the same
Real Vintage Gold Dust! A lot of old memories came flooding back! They don't make them like this any more! Again if your a fan of any of these girls, go for it!

Homemade DVDs that play once in a while and very frustrating to play.  I tried a NEW DVD player and the results were the same.  Package was cheap with a piece of paper over the original cover.  DVDs were stacked without anything separating the recorded surface from the disc underneath
